#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.1:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhaṇḍagāmavagga"
msgstr "1. At Bhaṇḍa Village"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Anubuddhasutta"
msgstr "1. Understood"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.1"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "an4.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "an4.1:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vajjīsu viharati bhaṇḍagāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Vajjis at the village "
"of Bhaṇḍa."

msgctxt "an4.1:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an4.1:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicants!”"

msgctxt "an4.1:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "an4.1:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.1:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ "
"dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, not understanding and not comprehending four things, both you "
"and I have wandered and transmigrated for such a very long time."

msgctxt "an4.1:2.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.1:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, sīlassa ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ "
"sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca."
msgstr "Noble ethics,"

msgctxt "an4.1:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ariyassa, bhikkhave, samādhissa ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ "
"dīghamaddhānaṃ sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca."
msgstr "immersion,"

msgctxt "an4.1:2.5"
msgid ""
"Ariyāya, bhikkhave, paññāya ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ "
"sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca."
msgstr "wisdom,"

msgctxt "an4.1:2.6"
msgid ""
"Ariyāya, bhikkhave, vimuttiyā ananubodhā appaṭivedhā evamidaṃ dīghamaddhānaṃ "
"sandhāvitaṃ saṃsaritaṃ mamañceva tumhākañca."
msgstr "and freedom."

msgctxt "an4.1:2.7"
msgid ""
"Tayidaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyaṃ sīlaṃ anubuddhaṃ paṭividdhaṃ, ariyo samādhi "
"anubuddho paṭividdho, ariyā paññā anubuddhā paṭividdhā, ariyā vimutti "
"anubuddhā paṭividdhā, ucchinnā bhavataṇhā, khīṇā bhavanetti, natthi dāni "
"punabbhavo”ti."
msgstr ""
"These noble ethics, immersion, wisdom, and freedom have been understood and "
"comprehended. Craving for continued existence has been cut off; the "
"attachment to continued existence is ended; now there are no more future "
"lives.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.1:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "an4.1:3.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.2"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.1"
msgid "“Sīlaṃ samādhi paññā ca,"
msgstr "“Ethics, immersion, and wisdom,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.2"
msgid "vimutti ca anuttarā;"
msgstr "and the supreme freedom:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.3"
msgid "Anubuddhā ime dhammā,"
msgstr "these things have been understood"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:4.4"
msgid "gotamena yasassinā."
msgstr "by Gotama the renowned."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.1"
msgid "Iti buddho abhiññāya,"
msgstr "And so the Buddha, having insight,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.2"
msgid "dhammamakkhāsi bhikkhunaṃ;"
msgstr "explained this teaching to the mendicants."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.3"
msgid "Dukkhassantakaro satthā,"
msgstr "The teacher made an end of suffering,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.1:5.4"
msgid "cakkhumā parinibbuto”ti."
msgstr "seeing clearly, he is extinguished.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.1:5.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
